### Get companies (paginated, with search/industry filter)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/companies?page=1&limit=10&search=tech&industry=Software
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get jobs of my company (based on logged-in user)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/companies/me/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get a single company by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new company (superAdmin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/companies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "OpenAI",
  "industry": "Software",
  "location": "San Francisco, USA",
  "size": "500+",
  "description": "AI research and deployment company",
  "website": "https://openai.com"
}

###

### Update a company (superAdmin or companyAdmin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "OpenAI Updated",
  "industry": "AI/ML",
  "location": "San Francisco",
  "size": "600+",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "website": "https://openai.com"
}

###

### Get jobs of a specific company
GET http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get company users (companyAdmin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add a user to a company (companyAdmin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roleId": 2
}

###

### Remove a user from a company (companyAdmin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/companies/1/users/5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
